trans-unit.source: Provides access to information received by the <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> class when accepting WebSocket connections.
trans-unit.target: Fornece acesso às informações recebidas pela classe <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> ao aceitar conexões WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Gets the cookies received by the <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> object in the WebSocket opening handshake.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os cookies recebidos pelo objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> no handshake de abertura de WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Net.CookieCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Net.CookieCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The cookies received by the <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Os cookies recebidos pelo <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Gets the HTTP headers received by the <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> object in the WebSocket opening handshake.
trans-unit.target: Obtém os cabeçalhos HTTP recebidos pelo objeto <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> no handshake de abertura de WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The HTTP headers received by the <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Os cabeçalhos HTTP recebidos pelo <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpListener" /> objeto.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates if the WebSocket client is authenticated.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o cliente do WebSocket está autenticado.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the WebSocket client is authenticated; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o cliente do WebSocket está autenticado; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates if the WebSocket client connected from the local machine.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o cliente do WebSocket se conectou do computador local.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the WebSocket client connected from the local machine; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se o cliente do WebSocket conectado no computador local; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that indicates if the WebSocket connection is secured using Secure Sockets Layer (SSL).
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se a conexão WebSocket é protegida usando SSL (protocolo SSL).

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the WebSocket connection is secured using SSL; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se a conexão WebSocket é protegida usando SSL; Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the Origin HTTP header included in the WebSocket opening handshake.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor do cabeçalho HTTP Origin incluído no handshake de abertura do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.String" />.

trans-unit.source: The value of the Origin HTTP header.
trans-unit.target: O valor do cabeçalho HTTP de origem.

trans-unit.source: Gets the URI requested by the WebSocket client.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o URI solicitado pelo cliente do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Uri" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Uri" />.

trans-unit.source: The URI requested by the WebSocket client.
trans-unit.target: O URI solicitado pelo cliente do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the SecWebSocketKey HTTP header included in the WebSocket opening handshake.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o valor do cabeçalho HTTP SecWebSocketKey incluído no handshake de abertura do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.String" />.

trans-unit.source: The value of the SecWebSocketKey HTTP header.
trans-unit.target: O valor do cabeçalho HTTP SecWebSocketKey.

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of the Secure WebSocket protocols included in the WebSocket opening handshake.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a lista de protocolos WebSocket incluídos no handshake de abertura do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Collections.Generic.IEnumerable`1" />.

trans-unit.source: The list of the Secure WebSocket protocols.
trans-unit.target: A lista dos protocolos WebSocket seguro.

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of sub-protocols requested by the WebSocket client.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a lista de subprotocolos solicitada pelo cliente do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.String" />.

trans-unit.source: The list of sub-protocols requested by the WebSocket client.
trans-unit.target: A lista de subprotocolos solicitada pelo cliente do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Gets an object used to obtain identity, authentication information, and security roles for the WebSocket client.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto usado para obter identidade, informações de autenticação e funções de segurança para o cliente WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal" />.

trans-unit.source: The identity, authentication information, and security roles for the WebSocket client.
trans-unit.target: A identidade, informações de autenticação e funções de segurança para o cliente do WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Gets the WebSocket instance used to send and receive data over the WebSocket connection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a instância WebSocket usada para enviar e receber dados pela conexão WebSocket.

trans-unit.source: Returns <see cref="T:System.Net.WebSockets.WebSocket" />.
trans-unit.target: Retorna <see cref="T:System.Net.WebSockets.WebSocket" />.

trans-unit.source: The WebSocket instance.
trans-unit.target: A instância WebSocket.
